{"tid":2329944,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟新辣招監管科網巨擘","createTime":"2020-12-17T14:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T15:52:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"25d28f86eb9b3e615f6e306e2e069242db237ecd","tid":2329944,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:59:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201217/KS7TL5H5EVH3BCQFNNINYASSHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201217%2FKS7TL5H5EVH3BCQFNNINYASSHA%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28SHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=507f16fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201217%2FKS7TL5H5EVH3BCQFNNINYASSHA%2F&h=8158be4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201217/KS7TL5H5EVH3BCQFNNINYASSHA/</a><br />\n<br />\n歐盟新辣招監管科網巨擘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rDJL6txaqSEyZyaLqUfM7jckMLs=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WYMYJTQMJNAUDBFO6WR2KBV3NM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrDJL6txaqSEyZyaLqUfM7jckMLs%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWYMYJTQMJNAUDBFO6WR2KBV3NM.jpg&h=8a0277d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■前日歐盟委員會大樓外有示威者戴上fb創辦人朱克伯格面具，高舉「管我吧」的標語。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟前日提出兩項新法案，加強監管facebook、亞馬遜及蘋果公司等大型科網企業，要求企業增加營運透明度和競爭性，打擊非法或不實內容等，違者面臨高達年收入10%的巨額罰款，甚至被勒令拆售。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n罰款可達年收入一成<br />\n<br />\n歐盟公佈的《數碼市場法》規定，企業須遵守要求防止不公平壟斷市場，違規者將被罰款或分拆，罰款最高可達企業年收入一成。至於《數碼服務法》就規定，逾4,500萬用戶的平台須制訂更多措施，應對非法內容、侵犯人權，及蓄意影響選舉結果及公共衞生等問題，違者最高被罰年收入6 %。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，歐盟將10間企業列作數碼把關者，受更嚴格監管的包括美國fb、Google、亞馬遜、蘋果、微軟和SnapChat，中國的阿里巴巴和字節跳動、<a href=\"http://南韓的三星和荷蘭酒店預訂平台Booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9F%E5%92%8C%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%82%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0Booking.com&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28SHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=b9e05aa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">南韓的三星和荷蘭酒店預訂平台Booking.com</a>。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟競爭事務專員維斯塔格稱，提案控制主導市場的數碼把關者，確保言論自由同時創造安全可靠服務。Google稱新例似乎專門針對少數公司，fb則指新例維護互聯網優勢，又希望規範蘋果公司不再壟斷網絡生態。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/路透社"},{"pid":"fef723cedd59ba7f51ea61079ce62f0108f7b519","tid":2329944,"uid":221171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T15:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4kwGtTG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4kwGtTG.jpg&h=521b80f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2XzQndJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2XzQndJ.gif&h=24ec00aa&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}